sequenceDiagram
  participant Web as Web UI
  participant App as App Runs API

  Web->>App: GET /api/runs?page=1&status=running
  App-->>Web: Runs list (paginated)
  Web->>App: GET /api/runs/{id}
  App-->>Web: Run detail
  Web->>App: PUT /api/runs/{id} (pause/resume)
  App-->>Web: Status updated
  Web->>Web: Deep-link to App for advanced history/streams
